SECURITY NOTICE:
This software handles sensitive credentials and system access. Users should:
- Follow all organizational security policies
- Implement appropriate access controls
- Regularly review audit logs
- Keep the software updated
- Report security issues promptly

For security vulnerabilities, please report through appropriate channels as
defined by your organization's security policies.